N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 733.2 - Designation of supervisory official

State Regulations

Each public utility or municipality subject to the
regulations in this Part shall designate one or more persons with official
responsibility to supervise the program for preservation and the authorized
destruction of its records. Notes
